{"tid":340134,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃附加賽首回合","createTime":"2017-07-29T15:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T07:26:41.000Z","uid":92376,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfadc197133aca1e80b7f3e521fa80457fc42099","tid":340134,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n12:00am 平井桃@TWICE vs 宋智孝<br />\n12:02am 田馥甄 vs 陳穎欣@SG<br />\n12:04am 林詩枝 vs 劉亦菲<br />\n12:06am Blake Lively vs M&eacute;lanie Laurent<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d53aa11bedefb1bd7344c1dc45c640d984cfed8","tid":340134,"uid":92376,"like":70,"dislike":52,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃附加賽首回合(附加賽兩回合勝方將獲最後四席分組賽名額)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-30 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aoVAjQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaoVAjQe.png&h=298f7f90&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d7v6kt6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd7v6kt6.png&h=cd80319e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8wi9x8R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8wi9x8R.png&h=30191877&s={SIZE}\" />平井桃@TWICE vs 宋智孝<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jtH2NRj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjtH2NRj.png&h=118bdad7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合附加賽設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"77a3f5271f236003d8c6cc3555a20f9efe31c728","tid":340134,"uid":92376,"like":40,"dislike":57,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-30 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vEiMk9Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvEiMk9Z.png&h=9be2f60e&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5CoutsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5CoutsX.png&h=a477a0c1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1VqtNWG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1VqtNWG.png&h=350339e8&s={SIZE}\" />田馥甄 vs 陳穎欣@SG<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BEoiKsq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBEoiKsq.png&h=501d905d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合附加賽設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"6f49124b5cabaffd0b59e7a153177859dd77ad34","tid":340